Package sjc.type

Provides for StaticJava type hierarchy.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NonPrimitiveType
    This interface represents a non-primitive type of an ArrayType in StaticJava.
    PrimitiveType
    This interface represents a primitive type of an ArrayType in StaticJava.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayType
    This class represents a one-dimensional array type in StaticJava.
    BaseType
    This class represents a base type of an ArrayType in StaticJava.
    BooleanType
    This class represents the boolean type in StaticJava.
    ClassType
    This class represents a class type in StaticJava.
    IntType
    This class represents the int type in StaticJava.
    NonBaseType
    This class represents a non-base type of an ArrayType in StaticJava.
    NullType
    This class represents the null type in StaticJava.
    Type
    This class represents a type in StaticJava.
    TypeFactory
    This class is used to build Types in StaticJava.
    VoidType
    This class represents the void type in StaticJava.
